Response ID: resp_2541
Response Text: I would like to see the programs opened to other arts organizations that, due to their very specific mission and expertise, can not really focus on serving specific underrepresented groups.   Also, I would like to see greatly improved applications (particularly for Elevate) that are more arts oriented and less like a social services application.  Finally, I would like to applications to be reviewed by people knowledgable about the specific discipline (say music, theater, visual arts).  Our application was reviewed by a panel that did not have knowledge of our art form and had serious misunderstandings that affected our scores).  I do think that arts funding needed to be expanded to underrepresented groups.  We expected funding to be reduced, but not completely eliminated (our group received funding for over 20 years).

